======================================================================
α₁ FOR REGULAR TOURNAMENTS ON n VERTICES
======================================================================
  n= 3: α₁ =    1, α₁ mod 2 = 1, α₁/n = 0.3
  n= 5: α₁ =    5, α₁ mod 2 = 1, α₁/n = 1.0
  n= 7: α₁ =   14, α₁ mod 2 = 0, α₁/n = 2.0
  n= 9: α₁ =   30, α₁ mod 2 = 0, α₁/n = 3.3
  n=11: α₁ =   55, α₁ mod 2 = 1, α₁/n = 5.0
  n=13: α₁ =   91, α₁ mod 2 = 1, α₁/n = 7.0

Simplified: α₁ = n(n²-1)/24
  n=3: α₁ = 3×8/24 = 3×0 = 1
  n=5: α₁ = 5×24/24 = 5×1 = 5
  n=7: α₁ = 7×48/24 = 7×2 = 14
  n=9: α₁ = 9×80/24 = 9×3 = 30
  n=11: α₁ = 11×120/24 = 11×5 = 55
  n=13: α₁ = 13×168/24 = 13×7 = 91

α₁ parity:
  n= 3: α₁=   1, even=False
  n= 5: α₁=   5, even=False
  n= 7: α₁=  14, even=True
  n= 9: α₁=  30, even=True
  n=11: α₁=  55, even=False
  n=13: α₁=  91, even=False
  n=15: α₁= 140, even=True
  n=17: α₁= 204, even=True
  n=19: α₁= 285, even=False

